data.description: Don't miss out on your chance to own a fantastic home in the desirable north end of Evansville. The main level features an open floor plan with 3 spacious bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms and a kitchen equipped with new stainless steel appliances. On the upper level you'll find the enormous 4th bedroom that would also be perfect for a kids playroom or a man cave. If you want a private backyard, this is the one for you! Imagine summer cookouts in solitude. The backyard has a privacy fence and backs up to the woods. Peace and quiet!
